According to fields notes the square mile is 467.9 that fall within the San Antonio city limits, this includes the surrounding cities within San Antonio, (Castle Hills, Terrell Hill, Olmos Park, Alamo Heights, Hill Country Village, Hollywood Park). Without the Cities and Lackland AFB, within San Antonio the total would reflect approximately 466.6 square miles. Last updated on 09/30/2009; ordinance #2009-06-18-0516
